    "body": "Hi Matt,\n\nBoth HBox and VBox are helper functions.  Sorry, I know this is misleading.  You can see their source code here: https://github.com/ipython/ipywidgets/blob/master/ipywidgets/widgets/widget_box.py#L70-L78 .\n\nYou can inherit from flexbox and pass the kwarg orientation = 'vertical' or 'horizontal' to the base constructor for the effect you are looking for..\n"
